Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE are pleased to offer Unit 15/22 Beaumont Road to market for sale via Expression of Interest.

Located in the popular Mount Kuring-Gai Industrial estate, this rare large Industrial strata unit has only ever been occupied by a single tenant.

With a newly signed 7 year lease in place, this property presents an unrivalled investment opportunity for an astute investor to capitalise on the continued strong growth provided by surrounding infrastructure improvements.

Key highlights include:

+ Net income of $255,735.08 pa
+ Secure investment with brand new lease to long standing tenant
+ Ideal 8m high clearance span warehouse
+ Functional well built unit in sought after estate
+ Location set to benefit from the North Connex infrastructure project
+ 40-foot container access and semi-trailer access

The property will be sold via an Expression of Interest (EOI) closing Thursday 25th July 2019 at 5pm

For more information or to arrange an inspection, please contact exclusive CBRE sales agents below: 

Ben Byford - 0414 722 935
Peter Mangraviti - 0413 750 350

Gateway Estate is located in the heart of Mt Ku Ring Gai Industrial precinct, within close proximity to Mt Ku Ring Gai train station, approximately 3 kilometres to the M1 motorway on-ramp and approximately 1 kilometre to the Pacific Highway.

Mt Ku Ring Gai now benefits from the NorthConnex Tunnel linking the M1 and the M2 motorway. This drastically reduces travel times between Mt Ku Ring Gai and Western Sydney. 

For Lease is this modern Industrial unit within a popular estate in the heart of Mt Ku Ring Gai.

+ High clearance office and warehouse unit
+ 7 to 8.7m* internal warehouse clearance 
+ 40ft container access
+ Available immediately
+ Competitive terms on offer
+ ESFR Sprinklers
+ Seldomly found unit size, won’t last long!

*approximate

For further details and to inspect, please contact exclusive agents CBRE
